Volunteer Assault Corps
Ties to PMC Redut

Consists of: 
21st battalion BARS (BARS-21) "Don";
Assault battalion "Egorlyk";
Battalion BARS "Aksai";
Reconnaissance battalion BARS "Khoper" with the company "Donets" attached to it;
Artillery division BARS "Manych";
6th battalion BARS (BARS-6) "Forstadt";
15th battalion BARS (BARS-15) "Ermak".
 with separate assault battalion BARS "Crimea".

Consists of:

2nd Cossack brigade "Dnepr", consisting of:

I. NN battalion BARS "Dnepr-Smolensk";
II. NN-th reconnaissance battalion BARS "Dnepr";
III. NN-th assault detachment "named after Hero of Russia Dmitry Polkovnikov";
IV. NN-th howitzer division BARS;
V. NN-th communications detachment and UAV "Orion".

Formed 2023: https://twitter.com/sovietarmyfan/status/1662880147697987588

Consists of 
I. 24th battalion BARS (BARS-24) "Terek";
III. 35th battalion BARS (BARS-35) “Skif” with the companies “Dniester” (aka “named after Prince Kantemir”), “Liakhva” and “named after Tygyn Darkhan” attached to it;
IV. NN-th reconnaissance detachment "Maestro";
V. NN battalion "Baltika" (formed from members of the Wagner PMC who transferred to BARS);
VI. NN battalion BARS "Yenisei";
VII. NN battalion "Donetsk";
VIII. NN International Battalion "Caspian".

Was 3rd Brigade, now 5th Recon Assault Terek

4th Volunteer reconnaissance and assault Cossack brigade "Siberia" (aka "Vostok-V"), consisting of:

I. NN battalion "Irtysh";
 II. NN-th battalion BARS "Siberia";
 III. NN-th reconnaissance battalion "Yenisei" (Not the same as the other Yenisei...)

Volunteer artillery "brigade" - likely battery, as of November 2023. Was downgraded to Regiment by 2025

Cossack artillery brigade "Volga", consisting of:
 I. NN-th artillery division BARS "Volga";
 II. NN-th howitzer division BARS "Pechora";
III. NN artillery division BARS "Listan";
 IV. NN artillery battalion BARS "Lugan";

Likely part of 4th MRB by 2025 and folded in to their card

Subordinate to 1st Air Division, 4th Air Army

Equipment: 1 units. Su-25SM3 (Presumably 01)
